casebody.data:
FIERRO
v.
LANDRY'S RESTAURANT S249487 Supreme Court of California. AUGUST 29, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The petition for review is granted, and the matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division One, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of China Agritech, Inc. v. Resh (2018) --- U.S. ---- [138 S.Ct. 1800, 201 L.Ed.2d 123]. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
